OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775721946
OL,3,CMan arrested as woman stabbed at
OL,4,Ccrematorium
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder after a woman was
OL,8,Fstabbed at a crematorium.
OL,10,FPolice were called to reports of an
OL,11,Fattack at Carleton Crematorium in
OL,12,FBlackpool at about 6.45pm on Tuesday.
OL,14,FA woman in her 30s received a number
OL,15,Fof stab wounds and was taken to
OL,16,Fhospital before she was later
OL,17,Fdischarged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
