CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775721946
OL,3,CMan arrested as woman stabbed at
OL,4,Ccrematorium
OL,6,FPolice said a man in his 30s was
OL,7,Farrested in nearby Low Moor Road
OL,8,Fshortly after the incident and remains
OL,9,Fin custody.
OL,11,FThe victim and the suspect were known
OL,12,Fto each other, police added.
OL,14,FDetective Inspector Chris Hammond, of
OL,15,FBlackpool police, said: "This assault
OL,16,Fleft the victim with a number of
OL,17,Finjuries and it is only a matter of
OL,18,Fgood fortune that she wasn't more
OL,19,Fseriously hurt or even killed.
OL,26,@wD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
